title: BRIEF-Australian Leaders Fund Announces Final Dividend Of 2.5 CPS And A $45 Million Share Buy Back

BRIEF-Australian Leaders Fund Announces Final Dividend Of 2.5 CPS And A $45 Million Share Buy Back

© Reuters. BRIEF-Australian Leaders Fund Announces Final Dividend Of 2.5 CPS And A $45 Million Share Buy Back Sept 27 (Reuters) - Australian Leaders Fund Ltd : * DECLARES A FINAL DIVIDEND OF 2.5 CENTS PER SHARE AND ANNOUNCES A $45 MILLION EQUAL ACCESS OFF-MARKET SHARE BUY BACK
